Subject: Unable to login to active directory authentication for sync of administrators
Description: I have created a service account for AD sync which works in the Active directory LDAP panel of the appliance. However when attempting to use the same service account for authentication for administrators I am receiving an error. The settings are the same, is there a known reason why this would not work?
Solution_Comment__c: we re-created the AD configuration, saved, and afterwards the administrators were synced
